{"tid":2172734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（轉貼）你地一係就一口咬定陳彥係俾政府謀殺，跟住正正經經諗辦法報仇。","createTime":"2020-08-24T22:56:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T04:01:05.000Z","uid":361255,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b097c33ca8b07d09b08deec52f4bbbfa41aeb36d","tid":2172734,"uid":361255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T22:56:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7289484/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F7289484%2Fpage%2F1&d=HUgUlm9NWlnA9xfyBh3Sbv3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=658c59a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7289484/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n你地一係就一口咬定陳彥係俾政府謀殺，跟住正正經經諗辦法報仇。<br />\n話有疑點有撚用咩？拖拖拉拉成年，咁有無證據？不斷討論一樣無答案嘅野，有撚用咩？<br />\n其實夠惡嘅話唔駛證據，你地有決心，一早報咗仇啦！再講，唔通查出陳彥林原來真係自殺，你地會回心轉意撐政府？！<br />\n又或者再掉返轉，有證據又點？<br />\n政府開記招：「係呀！我地做㗎！吹咩？」<br />\n你地做到d咩？大聲d唱多兩次榮光，擺多一千次路際，賣多100份蘋果？！<br />\n呢個咁嘅政府，有無陳彥林呢單野都要全面同佢死過㗎啦！咪撚再搵藉口啦！"},{"pid":"4fed5150fd42f82865eb5dc0736c106447f8ebad","tid":2172734,"uid":361255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T22:59:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1394b676133ed87744cd898f44bcce609998dd7c","tid":2172734,"uid":187232,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T01:06:02.000Z","msg":"有啲真相注定永遠搵唔到<br />\n但屬於陳彥霖嘅公義 我哋可以幫佢搵返黎"},{"pid":"331523de504d8a8bcba1f88726870c92cff8abb2","tid":2172734,"uid":58008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T01:08:37.000Z","msg":"本身連登仔淨係識唱歌<br />\n依家連唱歌 都無<br